body: "Scope: resolveEventEndAt + the relative-offset parser. Keep --deadline/relative-token semantics (m=months) unchanged for backward compat; introduce a distinct minutes token only for durations, or accept ISO-8601 duration. Update docs + completions. 100% cov."
